{"tid":1812200,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想問d野，求解夢師","createTime":"2020-01-05T10:06:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T15:24:33.000Z","uid":31311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"32b012c9e5a0e9934c5d2f95cb848d1628c5a35b","tid":1812200,"uid":31311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:06:33.000Z","msg":"發夢果陣諗到<br />\n<br />\n如果依加玩鳩拉嘅話，附近狗屋嘅狗一定會傾巢而出<br />\n<br />\n問題1:咁狗屋係咪得返一小部分嘅陣守住？<br />\n<br />\n問題2:狗屋果一小部分會唔會係老弱殘兵？<br />\n<br />\n有玩過AOE嘅大家應該都知，一出兵之後，大本營就會冇曬兵，如果要守返住個營都要即刻去練兵。<br />\n<br />\n人攻我守就只會輸，反而人攻我偷襲，逼佢地退兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個可塑性高唔高？"},{"pid":"4ab46cae9ff9740f7acb1122abe96d853a7e7a2e","tid":1812200,"uid":31311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:07:57.000Z","msg":"一個區大概三至四個狗屋"},{"pid":"ffcfd831bcfb207aab4f2001695c3207dca7fc3b","tid":1812200,"uid":236698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:08:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8bb20901867ee61f6ffaaeb93b4932c8fdd34df2","tid":1812200,"uid":236698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccca02617ec83adb17d57ab3312dbd0ccde75d4b","tid":1812200,"uid":31311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffcfd831bcfb207aab4f2001695c3207dca7fc3b","tid":1812200,"uid":236698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:08:41.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:10:06.000Z","msg":"去其他區行下街飲下啤酒都好"},{"pid":"3767821ff0bc4906a43a381e18b65501d4e1e4aa","tid":1812200,"uid":31311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:11:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b37ed076d14ce5c327d6b01fb04631b4c6706e80","tid":1812200,"uid":306621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:14:59.000Z","msg":"我有一個諗法，純討論，唔知work 唔work<br />\n遊行其中一個目的係裝修師傅做野<br />\n如果係遊行